'''The Burning Deck''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] on [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]] in the [[Corellian Sector (Nar Shaddaa)/Legends|Corellian Sector]]. Along with the [[Meltdown Café]] and [[Slag Pit/Legends|The Slag Pit]], it was one of the moon's three most popular [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] hangouts.

